claim.claim-text:
7. A method of manufacturing a detector comprising: 
depositing a solution containing a solvent and an analyte-sensing composition on a carrier, the analyte-sensing composition including an indicator dye, a buffer, and an osmotic control agent; 
removing the solvent; 
forming a hydrophobic barrier on a surface of the carrier; and 
placing an outer barrier on a surface of the carrier opposite the hydrophobic barrier.
